    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Throughout his career, Sanford I. Weill has vanquished rivals and also his closest allies. Now that Citigroup, the world's biggest money machine, is all his, the only person left to outdo is himself. A report by Roger Lowenstein in The Times Magazine.</p>
